# Astro pages & layouts

## Layout chain

`BaseLayout` → `PostLayout` | `ToolLayout` | `SeriesLayout` | `PageLayout`

- Put shared head/nav/ads/GA in `BaseLayout` only when global
- Tool pages: shell in Astro, interactivity in Svelte islands

## Content collections

Schemas live in `src/content.config.ts` (Zod). When adding frontmatter fields, update the schema first.

## Routing

- File routes under `src/pages/`
- Dynamic tools: `getStaticPaths` filters `published` tools
- Endpoints: `feed.xml.ts`, `search-index.json.ts` (prerendered JSON)

## Links & assets

```ts
const BASE = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
// ✅ `${BASE}tools/foo/`
// ❌ `/tools/foo/` when base may be `/pr-preview/pr-N/`
```

## Prod-only third parties

Gate AdSense/GA with `import.meta.env.PROD`. Testing builds use `NODE_ENV=development`.
